headline: Barclays Maintains Equal-Weight on Archer-Daniels-Midland, Raises Price Target to $68
summary: Barclays  analyst Benjamin Theurer   maintains Archer-Daniels-Midland (NYSE:ADM) with a Equal-Weight and raises the price target from $61 to $68.

headline: 2 S&P 500 Stocks to Target This Week and 1 We Find Risky
summary: The S&P 500 (^GSPC) is often seen as a benchmark for strong businesses, but that doesn’t mean every stock is worth owning. Some companies face significant challenges, whether it’s stagnating growth, heavy debt, or disruptive new competitors.
